CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 7, 1971, pg. 34 reads: "Mt. Carmel Models In Garden Fashion Fantasy - The beautiful lawn of Mt. Carmel Baptist Church, North Versailles Township, was the scene of a bright summer fashion fantasy. A brilliant array of ready-to-wear apparel for the young and the younger, and males as well, was on parade.  Smart models, pictured left to right are, Bill Varner, Alberta Corbitt, Gwendolyn Bowick, Patti Owens, Little Miss Elaine Venable, the pastor's daughter;...-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Bill Varner, Alberta Corbitt, Gwendolyn Bowick, Patti Owens, and Elaine Venable, posed in front of Mt. Carmel Baptist Church for Garden Fashion Fantasy, North Versailles
